(Photo: Jemal Countess, Getty Images) CONNECT TWEET   
R & B artist and actress Jill Scott finally makes a stop in Louisville. The "Get on Up" star is scheduled for Friday, December 11th at the Louisville Palace. The singer/songwriter released her latest album "Woman" earlier this year. She's actually in my current rotation of music I listen too daily. It's empowering, sassy and it tells a story of life. Tickets for the show go on sale today at 12 noon, (Oct 23rd). Tickets range from $49.50 to $99.50 for the 8:00 pm show.
